extra essentiel Components:
- Three Firewalls for security
- SSL Certificate for encrypted communication
- Three Monitoring Clients for performance data

Firewalls for:
- Blocking unauthorized access and cyber threats

Traffic served over HTTPS for:
- Protecting user data from attacks

Monitoring used for:
- Early detection of performance issues and security incidents

Monitoring tool collecting data:
- Tracks web server metrics like QPS

Issues with Infrastructure:
- SSL Termination at Load Balancer exposes decrypted traffic
- Single Point of Failure at Database Primary node
- Same components on each server can lead to inefficiency
